message.content:
Ewe, ndiyakunceda. Ndibuyekezele ngokwethetha Xhosa ukuze ndinikezele inkcazelo eyimfihlo.

1. Ukufaka isicelo sokungena kwinkqubo karhulumente:
   - Khulula usayizi we-intanethi wakho.
   - Phuma kwesayithi wokunye nendawo yokungena kwinkqubo karhulumente.
   - Fumana inkqubo karhulumente enokufakwa isicelo.
   - Hlela eli-website kwaye ufake isicelo sakho ngokwentlalo.
   - Xhumana ngenkcazelo yombhalo nobungqina bakho ukuze ubone ukuba isicelo sakho sayi kufanele.

2. Ukuthola impendulo ngokwenqaku:
   - Khulula usayizi we-intanethi wakho.
   - Phuma kwesayithi wokunye nendawo yokuthola impendulo.
   - Fumana impendulo enokuthola ngokwenqaku.
   - Hlela eli-website kwaye ufake inkcukacha yakho.
   - Xhumana ngenkcazelo yombhalo nobungqina bakho ukuze ubone ukuba ipendulo yakho iyakufanele.

3. Ukunceda abantu ngokwenza inkcukacha:
   - Khulula usayizi we-intanethi wakho.
   - Phuma kwesayithi wokunye nendawo yokunceda abantu.
   - Fumana inkcukacha evulekileyo yokunceda abantu.
   - Hlela eli-website kwaye ufake inkcukacha yakho.
   - Xhumana ngenkcazelo yombhalo nobungqina bakho ukuze ubone ukuba inkcukacha yakho iyakufanele.

Nceda ndikhumbule ke ukuba andikuchaza into yokuba ndithetha isiXhosa, kodwa ndifanele uk
